snippet.title: Tap Once, Swing Big - Homerun Clash 2: Legends Derby
snippet.description:
A home run slugfest featuring legendary batters you can play with one hand!

The legendary Albert Pujols is here to play ball!
See if you have what it takes to beat the legendary record held by Albert "The Machine" Pujols!
